Install the ESP32 USB driver: https://www.silabs.com/developers/usb-to-uart-bridge-vcp-drivers?tab=downloads
 - read CP210x_Universal_Windows_Driver_ReleaseNotes.txt

For the GUISlice library:
	- install the library
	- Go to src/GUIslice_config.h
	- uncomment:
		#include "../configs/esp-tftespi-default-notouch.h"

For editing the GUISliceBuilder project:
	- install https://github.com/ImpulseAdventure/GUIslice-Builder

When updating the GUISlice project, run "import_GUISliceMenu.py"